://twitter.com/truthteller_x1/status/2049212627692437658", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "India won\u2019t do commercial deals unless that deal also allows them to dump their excess population into the Country they are doing that deal with.", "last_comment_created": 1777433838616, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 6, "score_up": 49, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"twitter": {"quotedTweet": {"quotedTweet": false, "images": false, "linkEmbed": false, "replies": 0, "created": 1777359120000, "id": "2049018777963000127", "video": false, "poll": false, "user": {"profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/599273793035620352/FXtrGIBc_normal.jpg", "displayName": "Richard Rossow", "username": "RichardRossow"}, "content": "It often feels like: \n- 85% of Americans still think of India as a $400b economy \n- 14% of Americans realize its a $4t economy\n- < 1% of Americans picture India as a $20t economy\n\nThis last group realizes- building a strong U.S.-India commercial relationship is worth some effort.", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 673}, "images": false, "linkEmbed": false, "replies": 3, "created": 1777405337000, "id": "2049212627692437658", "video": {"preview": "https://pbs.twimg.com/amplify_video_thumb/2021604628144738304/img/daU3CISr6SuacJH1.jpg", "mpeg": "https://video.twimg.com/amplify_video/2021604628144738304/pl/1LalkbWPO08_hoeE.m3u8?tag=14&v=475", "aspectRatio": [16, 9], "heightRatio": 56, "type": "video/mp4", "url": "https://video.twimg.com/amplify_video/2021604628144738304/vid/avc1/480x270/-4bdQfABjqrhO1Lh.mp4?tag=14"}, "poll": false, "user": {"profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1836574529650593793/Qfc82RA9_normal.jpg", "displayName": "\ud83c\uddfa\ud83c\uddf8Truth Teller\ud83c\uddfa\ud83c\uddf8", "username": "truthteller_x1"}, "content": "One problem\u2026.\n\nIndia won\u2019t do commercial deals unless that deal also allows them to dump their excess population into the Country they are doing that deal with.\n\n", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 154}}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASZaW0fgX", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 37, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8588321, "raw_content": "Knowing that Trump is an obstacle they first tried to prevent Trump from being elected. UK's MI6 Integrity Initiative issued the Steele dossier to frame Trump as a Russian agent.  \n  \nThat failed.  \n  \nThen they abused NATO to use Ukraine as a proxy. Ukraine is not a NATO member and there is no obligation on members to join UK's war agenda.  \n  \nNow their king comes and tells Congress we must prepare for war with Russia. An ocean of bullshit came out of his mouth as he told Congress we must \"stand shoulder to shoulder as we always have\".\n\nUK has manipulated the US into their wars, see here:\n\nhttps://patriots.win/p/16aTa2w08p/  \n  \nhttps://patriots.win/p/16aTLtGI9p/the-people-maneuvering-us-into-w/c/4TrI4K7NMi1  ", "author": "perma-maga", "created": 1777432744088, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "magnokor", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "UK wants war with Russia but is too weak. Therefor they try to manipulate the US into war with Russia. ", "last_comment_created": 1777440280983, "content": "<p>Knowing that Trump is an obstacle they first tried to prevent Trump from being elected. UK's MI6 Integrity Initiative issued the Steele dossier to frame Trump as a Russian agent.</p>\n<p>That failed.</p>\n<p>Then they abused NATO to use Ukraine as a proxy. Ukraine is not a NATO member and there is no obligation on members to join UK's war agenda.</p>\n<p>Now their king comes and tells Congress we must prepare for war with Russia. An ocean of bullshit came out of his mouth as he told Congress we must &quot;stand shoulder to shoulder as we always have&quot;.</p>\n<p>UK has manipulated the US into their wars, see here:</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://patriots.win/p/16aTa2w08p/\" target=\"_blank\">https://patriots.win/p/16aTa2w08p/</a></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://patriots.win/p/16aTLtGI9p/the-people-maneuvering-us-into-w/c/4TrI4K7NMi1\" target=\"_blank\">https://patriots.win/p/16aTLtGI9p/the-people-maneuvering-us-into-w/c/4TrI4K7NMi1</a></p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 7, "score_up": 37, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2049188920663916616", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASZaUspWs", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 125, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8587562, "raw_content": "", "author": "DonsChair", "created": 1777408786200, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "NotYourMan", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASZaUspWs.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/FBIDirectorKash/status/2049188920663916616", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blu